java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public class LocationViewSettingUI
extends javax.swing.JFrame

LocationViewSettingUI is the companion view for the Location Setting Option dialog for ViewLocationFilter model class. LocationViewSettingUI contains all of the interface components needed to access model components of ViewLocationFilter object.

Author:
Sasiluk Ruangrongsorakai (sruangro@calpoly.edu)
